      "content": "It’s just... the \"reconnecting\" part feels impossible. My friends are mostly gone, and my family, they have their own lives. They don't want to spend their time listening to an old person moan about how much everything hurts. It feels like I'm just taking up space until the clock runs out. It feels a bit pointless, you know? Like I'm just waiting for a deadline that's moving slower and slower every year.",
